<td style="text-align: left;">In-memory objects</td>
<td style="text-align: left;">Application Memory & Database</td>
<td style="text-align: left;">Data is read from the database, processed by the business logic in <code>CIServico</code> or <code>CIActividades</code>, and then written back to the database.</td>
